I '''V. Anand''' or '''Anand Viswanathan''', a keraklang ausan dang '''Viswanathan Anand''' ({{lang-ta|விசுவநாதன் ஆனந்த்}}, {{IPA-ta|ʋiʃʋəˈn̪aːt̪ən ˈaːnən̪d̪|IPA}}; mibait  11 Dicembre 1969) metung yang [[International Grandmaster|Grandmaster]] a Indian king [[chess]] ampong kasalukuyang [[World Chess Championship|World Chess Champion]]. Mekatalima neng sinambut i Anand king World Chess Championship <ref>{{cite news| url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/more-sports/chess/Viswanathan-Anand-shows-the-heart-of-a-champion-in-winning-fifth-world-title/articleshow/13676009.cms | title=Viswanathan Anand shows the heart of a champion in winning fifth world title| date=30 May 2012}}</ref> (2000, 2007, 2008, 2010, 2012), at ya ing alang salungat a Kampeon ning Yatu manibat kanitang 2007. 

Ya ing tinalan king [[FIDE]] [[World Chess Championship]] manibat 2000 anggang 2002, anyang panaun e mepitna la king titulung pangyatu. Ya ing meging [[World Chess Championship 2007|alang sasalungat a Kampeon ning Yatu]] anyang 2007 at [[World Chess Championship 2008|pemingwa ne ing kayang titulu]] laban kang [[Vladimir Kramnik]] anyang 2008. Kaybat, matagumpe neng pemingwa ing kayang titulu  king [[World Chess Championship 2010]] laban kang [[Veselin Topalov]] ampo king [[World Chess Championship 2012]]<ref name="As of May, 2012">[http://moscow2012.fide.com As of May, 2012 – Official FIDE World Championship 2012 site]. Moscow2012.fide.com. Retrieved on 2012-05-31.</ref> laban kang [[Boris Gelfand]]. Antimong makalukluk a kampeon, arapan ne ing sumambut king datang a [[Candidates Tournament]] king  [[World Chess Championship 2013]].

Metung ya kareng anam a talapamyalung king kasalesayan a mekabalbal king markang 2800 i Anand king listaan a FIDE [[Elo rating system|rating]], at anyang Abril 2007 king edad a 37, ya ing meging [[List of FIDE chess world number ones|manimuna king yatu]] king mumunang pamikatagun.  Mekatalima ya kareng anam a pamikatagun king babo ning pamagranggung pangyatu, manibat Abril 2007 anggang Julio 2008, at telan ne ing mumunang ranggu king kabilugan kareng labing limang (15). Anyang Octubre 2008, milwal ya king ranggung mumunang atlu king mumunang pamikatagun manibat anyang Julio 1996. Ikwa neng pasibayung Anand ing mumunang ranggu king yatu anyang 1 Noviembre 2010, anyang simbut ne ing kasalukuyan a mumuna king yatung i [[Magnus Carlsen]] king Bilbao Masters, oneng sibli ne kang Carlsen ing posisyon a iti anyang Julio 2011.

I Anand ing meging mumunang grandmaster ning India anyang 1988.<ref name="More questions than answers">[http://www.research.ibm.com/deepblue/home/may11/story_3.html More questions than answers], research.ibm.com</ref> Ya murin ing mumunang tinanggap king [[Rajiv Gandhi Khel Ratna]] Award anyang 1991–92, ing pekamatas a dangalan ning India king pasiknangan. Anyang 2007, tinggap ne ing kadwang pekamatas a galal ning India para kareng sibilan,ing [[Padma Vibhushan]], at uli na nita, ya ing  mumunang tau king pasiknangan ing tinanggap king dangalan a ita king amlat ning India. 

Linarawan neng [[Lubomir Kavalek]] i Anand a pekamaleparan belwan a kampeon ning yatu king kabilugan ning panaun ("the most versatile world champion ever"), uling bukud mung i Anand kareng sablang talapamyalung ing sinambut king kampeonatong pangyatu kareng dakal a format, kayabe ya ing [[Tournament chess|Tournament]], [[Match (chess)|Match]], [[Rapid chess|Rapid]], ampong [[Knockout competition|Knockout]] chess.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/lubomir-kavalek/chess-champions-class-act_b_768397.html |title=Lubomir Kavalek: Chess Champion's Class Act |work=Huffington Post |date= 23 October 2010|accessdate=11 November 2010}}</ref>

